37
00:01:27,920 --> 00:01:28,239
[SPEAKER_02] Patrick.

38
00:01:28,480 --> 00:01:38,480
[SPEAKER_01] Da, ja sam Patrick Rice, suosnivač i izvršni direktor Encounter Ministries koji se nalazi u biskupiji Lansing u Brightonu u Michiganu.

39
00:01:39,200 --> 00:01:42,079
[SPEAKER_01] I oženio sam se, moja supruga se zove Emily.

40
00:01:42,400 --> 00:01:45,519
[SPEAKER_01] Upoznali smo se na fakultetu na Franciscan University of Steubenville.

41
00:01:45,599 --> 00:01:47,280
[SPEAKER_01] Diplomirali smo 2006.

42
00:01:47,840 --> 00:01:47,920
[SPEAKER_01] godine.

43
00:01:49,840 --> 00:01:50,480
[SPEAKER_01] Šestero djece.

44
00:01:50,640 --> 00:01:51,840
[SPEAKER_01] Od petnaest do dvije godine.

45
00:01:52,239 --> 00:01:55,599
[SPEAKER_01] I to je dječak, djevojčica, djevojčica, djevojčica, dječak.

46
