47
00:01:56,400 --> 00:01:57,840
[SPEAKER_02] Koliko je staro najstarije dijete?

48
00:01:58,079 --> 00:01:59,040
[SPEAKER_01] Najstarije je sada petnaest.

49
00:01:59,359 --> 00:01:59,920
[SPEAKER_01] Najmlađe?

50
00:02:00,079 --> 00:02:00,239
[SPEAKER_01] Dva.

51
00:02:00,640 --> 00:02:02,799
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, puno spavate, zar ne?

52
00:02:03,120 --> 00:02:03,200
[SPEAKER_01] Ne.

53
00:02:04,319 --> 00:02:04,799
[SPEAKER_02] Dobro je.

54
00:02:04,799 --> 00:02:06,640
[SPEAKER_02] U redu, divno, divno, u redu.

55
00:02:07,920 --> 00:02:08,240
[SPEAKER_00] Tony?

56
00:02:08,560 --> 00:02:08,639
